  "comment": "LED PAR 54X3W RGB 3in1: Compact, vibrant, and efficient — the PAR 150 RGB brings bold colour to your stage. Featuring 54 x 3W RGB 3-in-1 LEDs, this lightweight fixture delivers stunning output with smooth colour blending. Its durable die-cast aluminium body and advanced heat dissipation ensure stable, long-lasting performance.\nWith flexible lens angle options and both 4CH (Basic) and 8CH (Standard) DMX control modes, it adapts to a wide range of professional setups. Ideal for DJs, stage shows, exhibitions, or ambient lighting — the PAR 150 RGB is built for impact.\n",
